file_content.text: What shall it be? Does one die? Do both?
Kill her! That was our deal--kill her!
You horrible worm....
You are both wretched.
And now you. Here to rescue the woman and the traitor. I am Ukabi.
I am your destruction.
Face your doom.
You're about to burn, little cyborg. How do your parts handle electricity?
Face your doom.
You and I have business together. Shall we?
Face-to-face at last.
You led a good hunt. Now it's over.
You're my target.
Godoba--he brought you here and sold us out?
The Hutt's a traitor?
Godoba and the others fear me. Fear destroys minds.
I'm giving you one chance. Step away from those two. Now.
Let Maro and Godoba free.
No.
Look upon my body. Cortosis skin grafts. Intravenous kolto injection system. Holographic targeting array.
You are only mortal. I will always prevail.
Death is coming for you.
